{"id": "firmware-development--on-demand-gps-activation-for-remote-telemetry-requests", "title": "On-Demand GPS Activation for Remote Telemetry Requests", "forum": "firmware-development", "messages": [{"id": "1467937804666274004", "author": "Bino", "author_handle": "thebino", "user_id": "279185063445528579", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Monday, February 2, 2026 12:40 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-02 12:40 p.m.", "text": "I created a Draft-PR where I added this idea as feature already. https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1564 I figured it does not need to be specific for a single variant, so I had to start a little refactoring first, I have some linker errors left, but the idea should be pretty much complete https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1571 Would like to get some feedback and support from experienced devs here.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I created a Draft-PR where I added this idea as feature already.\n<a href=\"https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1564\">https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1564</a>\n\nI figured it does not need to be specific for a single variant, so I had to start a little refactoring first, I have some linker errors left, but the idea should be pretty much complete\n<a href=\"https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1571\">https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1571</a>\n\nWould like to get some feedback and support from experienced devs here.</span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-color-pill style=background-color:rgba(30,35,39,255)></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://github.com/meshcore-dev/MeshCore/pull/1564><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">On-Demand GPS Activation for Remote T